<p>I have an input text, and when you press enter, it's suppose to make the input text uneditable, before making it editable again in 3 seconds. But it's not working for some reason. What am I doing wrong? Thanks.</p>  <pre><code>&lt;input type = "text" id = "text"&gt;  &lt;script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.11.3/jquery.min.js"&gt;&lt;/script&gt; &lt;script type = "text/javascript"&gt;  $(function(){  $("#text").keyup(function(e){      if (e.which == 13) {     $("#text").prop("readonly", true);     setTimeout(function(){     $("#text").prop("readonly", false); }, 3000);  }); //end of if (e.which == 13)  }); //end of $(function())  &lt;/script&gt; </code></pre>